27#ifndef UV_THREADPOOL_H_
28#define UV_THREADPOOL_H_
29
30struct uv__work {
31 void (*work)(struct uv__work *w);
32 void (*done)(struct uv__work *w, int status);
33 struct uv_loop_s* loop;
34 void* wq[2];
35};

37#endif /* UV_THREADPOOL_H_ */
